BFN 

<F P=106> [POSTFACTUM report: "`People's Alliance' Patriotic Movement </F>
Created"] 
  [Text] A group of political figures came forward yesterday 
with a statement about the creation of a new Russian patriotic 
movement, the "People's Alliance." One of the movement's 
masterminds, Dmitriy Olshanskiy, has said that preparations for 
its establishment have been in progress since early January. 
The statement reads: "We come forward with an initiative to 
unite the patriotic intelligentsia, all citizens of Russia. We 
consider as the paramount task the shaping of a policy and 
tactics of national reconciliation." The document is signed by 
Sergey Glazyev, Dmitriy Olshanskiy, Oleg Rumyantsev, Yuriy 
Boldyrev, and others. 

